                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Ok, here is what I've gathered so far...<br /><br /><b>Sage Gunyth (South Tower) combines:</b><br />39th Level - Lesser Conjuration Earth, Wandering Mind, Invisiblility To Undead(wiz), and Chilling Embrace = Aqi Note = Tailsman of Research<br /><br />44th Level - Boon of Garou, Corpal Empathy, Elemental Maelstrom and Enticement of Flame =  Bep Note = Amulet of Knowledge<br /><br />49th Level note found.  Allure, Bond of Death, Greater Conjuration Fire, Warth of Al'Kabar = Cjo Note = Book of Forgotten Magic<br /><br />50th Level spells. Combining Translocate, Improved Invis, IItu, and Monster Summon II  =  Da note = Arcane quill<br /><br />51st Level spells. Atols, Splurt, Theft of Thought and Gift of Xev = Eio Note = Gem of Flowing Breath<br /><br />Bring Balic's research to Onirelin Gali, and Xelrin's research to Xasri Virek.<br /><br /><br /><b>Sage Balic (East Tower) combines:</b><br />29th Level - Rune of the Combine + Words of Possession = Rune of Combine = Sage's Apprentice Cap <br /><br />34th Level  - Rune of Sorcery + Words of Duress = Word of Sorcery = Twisted Talisman<br /><br />39th Level - Rune of the Helix + Words of Suffering = Rune of Helix = Three Ringed Hoop<br /><br />44th Level - Rune of Attraction?? + ?? = ?? (possibly broken atm)<br /><br />49th Level - Rune of Impetus + Words of Bondage = Word of Impetus = Apprentice's Notebook<br /><br />Bring Xelrin's research to Tenada and Gunyth's research to Winon.<br /><br /><br /><b>Sage Xelrin's (North Tower) combines:</b><br />Short Sword of the Ykesha = Spell: Ykesha = Gleaming Bauble<br /><br />Polished Granite Tomahawk = Spell: Berserker Strength?? = Flawed Spell Creation<br /><br />Screaming Mace = Spell:Screaming Mace = Sentient Medallion<br /><br /><b>Items that have been tried for combines </b><br />Beetle Stinger - DNC<br />Cat o Nine Tails - DNC<br />Crookstinger - DNC<br />Dagger of Dropping - DNC<br />Dragon Horn Ykesha - DNC<br />Ebony Bladed Sword - DNC<br />Gnoll Hide Lariat - DNC<br />Hammer of Rage - DNC<br />Icy Sword - DNC<br />Incandescent Wand - DNC<br />Obsidian Shard - DNC <br />Serrated Bone Dirk - DNC<br />Smoldering Brand - DNC<br />Spine Chill Spear - DNC<br />Stiletto of the Bloodclaw - DNC<br />Tentacle Whip - DNC<br />Velium Dagger - DNC<br />Velium Longsword - DNC<br />Velium Warhammer - DNC<br />Venomous ax of the something - DNC<br />Wakizashi of the Frozen Skys - DNC<br />Whip of Strangulation - DNC<br /><br />Bring research from Balic to Bolcen, and Gunyth's research to Acomar. <br /><br /><b>Questions to be answered that I see...</b><br />#1  Is there a Sage in the West tower who has yet to be discovered?<br />#2  Has anyone tried giving a note or Rune/Word reward to an assistant instead of the main guy?<br />#3  Why the hell is Wizard Invisiblity to Undead so flipping expensive?<br />#4  Xelrin Combines, has anyone tried Temple of Ro Quest items?  <br />#5  Just found Sathir's Wand, going to try that when I get home tonight.<br /><br /><br /><br /><center><br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=95266" target="_blank"><h4><font color=red>Kuotat Smith</h4></a>Baroness <s>Warlock</s> Witch<br />Mithaniel Marr</font id=red><br /></center><br /></span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
